{"tid":1221524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 賣港鐵證 ]林鄭獲頒法國最高榮譽 Officer of the Legion of Honor","createTime":"2019-06-14T08:32:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T08:33:12.000Z","uid":103207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8cc6a621e4ef24049e34c5500ce4c41e95026203","tid":1221524,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:32:25.000Z","msg":"//呢個聯署，真係一定要join，同埋推俾多d人<br />\n<br />\n原來<span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭係 2015 年獲頒法國最高榮譽 Officer of the Legion of Honor，表揚佢作為一個「模範政治領導人和公僕」既工作，同埋佢對於法國係香港既經濟及文化活動既支持</span>。四年後既今日我相信大家聽落去都覺嘔心。而<span style=\"color: red;\">法國Legion of Honor寫到明話如果有人得到呢個榮譽後做一D違背法國支持既理念（如自由，人權）既野，佢可以被取消資格的</span>。請大家聯署，要求法國當局取消林鄭呢個榮譽。自由，平等同博愛，佢配唔起！//<br />\n<br />\n來源 : fb<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/the-grand-chancery-of-the-legion-of-honor-revoke-hong-kong-chief-executive-carrie-lam-s-legion-of-honor-distinction-1401f615-a42b-4485-9cd2-5a7cab597c8c?recruiter=209664511&amp;utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_medium=facebook&amp;utm_campaign=psf_combo_share_abi&amp;recruited_by_id=844e6b50-9951-11e4-8539-531673214b14&amp;utm_content=fht-16099369-en-us%3Av6&amp;fbclid=IwAR0hhCcjnPn76lTEhnFCYuxV04RjTTnB0W-pXrXATCNdp_RgThRsxk12XrA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fthe-grand-chancery-of-the-legion-of-honor-revoke-hong-kong-chief-executive-carrie-lam-s-legion-of-honor-distinction-1401f615-a42b-4485-9cd2-5a7cab597c8c%3Frecruiter%3D209664511%26utm_source%3Dshare_petition%26utm_medium%3Dfacebook%26utm_campaign%3Dpsf_combo_share_abi%26recruited_by_id%3D844e6b50-9951-11e4-8539-531673214b14%26utm_content%3Dfht-16099369-en-us%253Av6%26fbclid%3DIwAR0hhCcjnPn76lTEhnFCYuxV04RjTTnB0W-pXrXATCNdp_RgThRsxk12XrA&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpAsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=1dcc975e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/the-grand-chancery-of-the-legion-of-honor-revoke-hong-kong-chief-executive-carrie-lam-s-legion-of-honor-distinction-1401f615-a42b-4485-9cd2-5a